commit_message:
Removing back-end usage from guest code

Reason:
 - guestagent should be free from direct Trove back-end DB connection.
Changes:
 - extending conductor API;
 - mysql guestaget service now reports through conductor;
 - removing from init script db_api initializing;
 - tests.

